    <div class="qode-accordion-content-inner">
        <div class=ordered></p>
<ol>
<li>Apply online.</li>
<li>We&#8217;ll reach out to you within 5-10 business days:
<ol>
<li><strong>No insurance?</strong> We’ll schedule your appointment right away</li>
<li><strong>Have insurance?</strong> We’ll work with them to figure out what’s covered. Don’t worry, 50 Legs will cover the rest.</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>You’ll go to one of our partner prosthetic facilities for 7–14 days to get professionally fitted. We cover the cost of your hotel and flights.</li>
<li>You’ll leave our trusted provider with your finished legs and no bills!</li>
</ol>
<p></div>    </div>
